snippet.title: The Final Station - Year 106 Trailer
snippet.description:
Pre-Order on Steam - http://store.steampowered.com/app/435530

It's been 106 years since the world changed forever. Now life is different. Travel by train through this dying world, discover new stations, take care of your passengers and do anything it takes to survive. The story-driven post-apocalyptic adventure is coming on August 30th. 

Follow on twitter - http://twitter.com/tinyBuild http://twitter.com/TheFinalStation
